Bootstrap: localimage
From: ./ubuntu_22.04.sif

%post
    set -e

    # Update package lists
    apt-get update

    # Install Python and pip
    DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
        python3 \
        python3-pip

    # Install pytest for the test suite
    pip3 install --no-cache-dir pytest

    # Create the required writable home directory for the student
    mkdir -p /home/user
    # Ensure it is writable by any non-root user that may run the container
    chmod 0777 /home/user

    # Clean up apt caches to reduce image size
    apt-get clean
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

%labels
    chmod 755 /home/user

    Author="Automated Build"
    Description="Environment for the backup reference-moment task. Includes pytest and a writable /home/user directory."

%help
    This container supplies the initial state for the “backup reference moment”
    exercise.  It provides:
      • Python 3 and pytest
      • A writable /home/user directory
    No additional files are pre-created, so the learner can complete the task
    by issuing the required single command.